  "moments": [
    {
      "id": "mo_001",
      "text": "Roja (song) triggers childhood memories—running in my Chennai neighborhood, my mom played it on loop while cooking. Just the first few notes make me smell cardamom and feel like I'm 7 again.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_002",
      "text": "Thuli Thuli (song) by Yuvan Shankar Raja takes me back instantly—danced to it in a hotel room during a Kerala trip; now every time I hear it, I'm instantly there.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_003",
      "text": "Enna Solluthen (song) brings me back to my aunt's terrace with cousins eating vadais, the breeze, the sunset—like a whole mini-vacation in a song.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-01",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_004",
      "text": "The monsoon petrichor smell ('vazhuthu') instantly calms Neha—when work stress hits, stepping outside to breathe it in brings immediate reset.",
      "tone": "grateful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_005",
      "text": "Ginger tea + lofi track with soft rain sounds and indie guitar hum + two-minute mindfulness breathing while watching rain from the window—that's Neha's tried-and-true ritual for centering herself when everything feels chaotic.",
      "tone": "content",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mo_006",
      "text": "Even when presentation slides are shifting and deadlines loom, Neha steadies herself with tiny anchors—'the rain's still falling, the coffee's still hot.' Small truths that ground her.",
      "tone": "hopeful",
      "sensitive": false,
      "first_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "last_seen": "2026-05-22",
      "mentions": 1
    }
  ],
